data.description: Welcome to your New home in The Estates of Beacon Woods Golf and Country Club! This bright and spacious 2010 sq ft 3/2/2 home is a true gem that invites you to experience comfortable and luxurious living. This home offers not only a place to live but a lifestyle to cherish, offering a spacious living area adorned with cathedral ceilings, a wide-open floor plan that bathes in natural sunlight, creating a warm and inviting ambiance throughout.  One of the highlights of this residence is the beautiful heated pool with a cascading waterfall spa, equipped with a New Electrical System and the temperature and water flow can all be cell phone controlled! A true oasis right in your backyard. Imagine unwinding in the hot tub or floating in the pool,  surrounded by tranquility and the beauty of your own private paradise. The pool lanai provides a perfect retreat after a long day, making it an ideal space for entertaining or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine. Great for Entertaining!(The pool pavers were recently regrouted and power washed, the front driveway pavers and walkway were recently resealed and power washed). Home also has a well for the irrigation.  Inside, the home has a large master suite, complete with a spacious ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet & access to the pool with a great view. The two guest bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfortable spaces for family or guests. The guest bathroom features a convenient shower-tub combo. The kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with Newer/Modern Appliances with ample counter space for preparing delicious meals. The expansive inside laundry room is an added convenience, featuring New Washer and Dryer, mini fridge, mini freezer and a laundry sink and extra storage for your organizational needs. The roof was completed in 2016, and the HVAC system is from 2013, new hurricane rated garage door, new water heater and new water softener as well.   As part of The Estates of Beacon Woods Golf and Country Club, you'll have access to a wealth of community amenities, including a recreation facility, fitness center, community swimming pool, playground, walking/bike pathways, public golf course, shuffleboard court and tennis courts. Also, with the HOA covering the cable TV, internet, trash and ground maintenance, you can enjoy a maintenance-free lifestyle and spend more time savoring the luxurious offerings of both your home and the community. Property has been repaired/remediated for ground settlement and is fully insureable!    Don't miss the chance to make this wonderful property your own. Schedule a visit today and start envisioning the incredible lifestyle that awaits you in this beautiful home!
